Important Note for Google Drive Videos:
Set Permissions: In Google Drive, you must right-click the video, select "Share," and change General access to "Anyone with the link can view." If it's set to "Restricted," the game will skip the video because it cannot access it.

Paste your link: Find the const DRIVE_LINK at the top of the <script> section (around line 177) and paste your sharing link there.

Third-Party Cookies: Some browsers block Google Drive streaming in iframes unless you are logged into Google or have certain privacy settings disabled. The code includes a fallback to just start the game if the video fails to load.

